title: Tea Pot
description:
HTC Touch - in High Definition. Watch music videos and streaming content in awe-inspiring high definition clarity for a mobile experience you never thought possible. Seductively sleek, the HTC Touch HD provides the next generation of mobile functionality, all at a simple touch. Fully integrated with Windows Mobile Professional 6.1, ultrafast 3.5G, GPS, 5MP camera, plus lots more - all delivered on a breathtakingly crisp 3.8' WVGA touchscreen - you can take control of your mobile world with the HTC Touch HD.


###### Features

- Processor Qualcomm® MSM 7201A™ 528 

- Windows Mobile® 6.1 Professional Operating 

- Memory: 512 MB ROM, 288 MB 

- Dimensions: 115 mm x 62.8 mm x 12 mm / 146.4 

- 3.8-inch TFT-LCD flat touch-sensitive screen with 480 x 800 WVGA 

- HSDPA/WCDMA: Europe/Asia: 900/2100 MHz; Up to 2 Mbps up-link and 7.2 Mbps down-link 

- Quad-band GSM/GPRS/EDGE: Europe/Asia: 850/900/1800/1900 MHz (Band frequency, HSUPA availability, and data speed are operator dependent

- Device Control via HTC TouchFLO™ 3D & Touch-sensitive front panel 

- GPS and A-GPS 

- Bluetooth® 2.0 with Enhanced Data Rate and A2DP for wireless stereo 

- Wi-Fi®: IEEE 802.11 b/

- HTC ExtUSB™ (11-pin mini-USB 2.0

- 5 megapixel color camera with auto 

- VGA CMOS color 

- Built-in 3.5 mm audio jack, microphone, speaker, and FM 

- Ring tone formats: AAC, AAC+, eAAC+, AMR-NB, AMR-WB, QCP, MP3, WMA, 

- 40 polyphonic and standard MIDI format 0 and 1 (SMF)/SP 

- Rechargeable Lithium-ion or Lithium-ion polymer 1350 mAh 

- Expansion Slot: microSD™ memory card (SD 2.0 compatible

- AC Adapter Voltage range/frequency: 100 ~ 240V AC, 50/60 Hz DC output: 5V and 

- Special Features: FM Radio, G-Sensor
